Package de.prototypefund.en16931.type

Enum SemanticDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SemanticDataType>
      • de.prototypefund.en16931.type.SemanticDataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Type, Serializable, Comparable<SemanticDataType>
    public enum SemanticDataType
extends Enum<SemanticDataType>
implements Type
    This enum contains all possible data types of the semantic part of the table within the EN 16931 specification.
